      },
      "date": "2017-10-19 10:39:58.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nI checked the code, and there are a large number of CLASSERTs.  I'd prefer have this patch do the change from LASSERT() to CLASSERT(), and then have a separate per-subsystem patch to mass replace CLASSERT() with BUILD_BUG_ON(), especially since they have the logic reversed and it is easy to mess that up.",
